`K·µ• ‚Üí L_w` lying above `K ‚Üí L`. Here we actually use the type synonyms `WithVal K` and `WithVal L`.
-/
noncomputable def adicCompletionComapSemialgHom (v : HeightOneSpectrum A) (w : HeightOneSpectrum B)
